T1  - Buy, Keep, or Sell: Economic Growth and the Market for Ideas
AU  - Akcigit, Ufuk
AU  - Celik, Murat Alp
AU  - Greenwood, Jeremy
Y1  - 2016/05/01
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/05/01
